         !text "An Interstellar Transport carrying power"
         !text "transfusion waste collided with a       "
         !text "meteor, scattering its contents towards "
         !text "Earth's Sun. Your mission is to deliver "
         !text "the chemical seeds of a protective      "
         !text "compound that will render the waste     "
         !text "harmless.                               "
         !text "                                        "
         !text "Your destination is Observation Labport "
         !text "5V. During the otherwise routine voyage,"
         !text "however, your ship was ensnared by a    "
         !text "tractor beam and forced to land on the  "
         !text "planetoid Oo-Topos. Hostile aliens      "
         !text "boarded your ship and threw you in a    "
         !text "prison cell. You must escape and recover"
         !text "your ship with its valuable cargo.      "
         !fill $40
